* Summing (inverting) op-amp, 3 inputs
Va ina 0 DC 1.07
Vb inb 0 DC 0.92
Vc inc 0 DC 0.43
Ra ina minus 22k
Rb inb minus 22k
Rc inc minus 22k
Rf out minus 100k
.subckt IDEAL_OPAMP in+ in- out
Rin in+ in- 1000Meg
E1 out 0 in+ in- 1e6
.ends IDEAL_OPAMP

X1 0 minus out IDEAL_OPAMP
.op
.print dc V(out)
.end